OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism police told ITV News
OL,7,FBurns was radicalised by what she'd
OL,8,Fseen online.
OL,10,FWarning: Some readers may find details
OL,11,Fin this article distressing
OL,13,FA neo-Nazi obsessed teenager who tried
OL,14,Fto behead a Kurdish barber with an axe
OL,15,Fbecause she wanted to "kill all Jews
OL,16,Fand Muslims" has been jailed for more
OL,17,Fthan 15 years.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
