PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FAlina Burns, 19, attacked Mohammed
OL,7,FMahmoodi, 27, as he stood outside the
OL,8,Fshop in Bedminster, Bristol, last
OL,9,FAugust.
OL,11,FBristol Crown Court heard Burns had
OL,12,Fbeen motivated by neo-Nazi extremism
OL,13,Fand had been in contact with far-right
OL,14,Fgroups.
OL,16,FShe had told a man on a dating app to
OL,17,F"kill all Jews and Muslims" and had
OL,18,Fsearched for information online about
OL,19,FJihad, the Southport stabbings, Jewish
OL,20,Fsupremacy and Nazi Germany.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FSerena Gates KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt: "The prosecution case is that
OL,8,Fthe defendant had an extreme right-
OL,9,Fwing mindset and wanted Jews and
OL,10,FMuslims to be killed and non-whites to
OL,11,Fflee or be expelled from the UK.
OL,13,F"The day before the attack the
OL,14,Fdefendant was watching videos of SS
OL,15,Fmarches and sent an email called, 'The
OL,16,Fdawn of civil war'."
OL,18,FCCTV footage shows Burns in a fast-
OL,19,Ffood restaurant in the hours before
OL,20,Fthe attack.
OL,26,@oD@HOUuD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FAt a previous hearing, Burns, of
OL,7,FLynton Road, Bristol, pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto attempted murder and three charges
OL,9,Fof having an article with a blade or
OL,10,Fpoint ` specifically an axe, a scalpel
OL,11,Fand two darts.
OL,13,FShe had denied a charge of engaging in
OL,14,Fconduct in preparation of terrorist
OL,15,Facts, contrary to the Terrorism Act.
OL,17,FThe Crown argued that despite
OL,18,Faccepting the pleas, there remained a
OL,19,Fterrorist motivation to the attack,
OL,20,Fwhich was accepted by the judge, Mrs
OL,21,FJustice Lambert.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FPassing sentence, the judge said: "I
OL,7,Fhave no doubt that you are a dangerous
OL,8,Foffender and you remain deeply
OL,9,Fentrenched in your abnormal belief
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,F"You communicated with a man on an
OL,13,Fonline dating app which at one stage
OL,14,Fyou expressed the desire to kill all
OL,15,Fthe Jews and Muslims in Britain, and
OL,16,Falso carry out a plan where you wished
OL,17,Fto take all the glory for carrying
OL,18,Fthis out.
OL,26,@nD@cOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
