OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,F"There were Telegram chats with the
OL,7,FPatriotic Alternative, a far-right
OL,8,Fgroup. The leader of the Patriotic
OL,9,FAlternative has made highly racist and
OL,10,Fhomophobic comments in public.
OL,12,F"You also accessed large quantities of
OL,13,Fmaterial reflecting extreme right-wing
OL,14,Fideology."
OL,16,FThe judge said Burns passed the
OL,17,Fthreshold for an extended sentence for
OL,18,Fdangerousness.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
