OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FShe imposed a custodial sentence of 15-
OL,7,Fand-a-half years and an additional
OL,8,Ffour-year period on licence. Burns
OL,9,Fwill be able to apply for parole after
OL,10,Fserving two thirds of the prison
OL,11,Fsentence.
OL,13,FBurns remained silent during this
OL,14,Finterview with police.
OL,16,FThe incident happened on 2 August when
OL,17,FBurns approached Mr Mahmoodi from
OL,18,Fbehind and swung the axe ` that she
OL,19,Fhad bought for the attack ` at his
OL,20,Fneck, causing a small wound.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FMr Mahmoodi, who was much bigger than
OL,7,Fthe 5ft 2in Burns, was able to wrestle
OL,8,Fthe axe away from her before she could
OL,9,Fstrike him again.
OL,11,FA nearby police officer heard the
OL,12,Fcommotion and went to the scene in
OL,13,FEast Street and arrested Burns.
OL,15,FAsked why she had attacked the Kurdish-
OL,16,FIranian man, Burns told the officer:
OL,17,F"Because I wanted to cut his neck. I
OL,18,Fwould do it again, but to succeed."
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
