PN,43409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FShe later told a Mental Health Act
OL,7,Fassessor she knew Mr Mahmoodi worked
OL,8,Fin the barbers, which was involved "in
OL,9,Fmoney laundering".
OL,11,F"I know of him, he works in the
OL,12,FTurkish barbers, I think they are
OL,13,Fmoney laundering and the police aren't
OL,14,Fdoing anything about it," she said.
OL,16,F"So if I done this, then maybe the
OL,17,Fpolice would investigate the shop."
OL,26,@pD@dOUqD@QO]sD@AOUvD@YO]xD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
