PN,43410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FMiss Gates told the court: "She
OL,7,Ffurther asked if it had been on the
OL,8,Fnews yet. She said she wanted to
OL,9,Finfluence people to do the same thing,
OL,10,Fbut be successful. She stated she
OL,11,Fwould do it again, but to succeed."
OL,13,FAfter Burns was arrested, police
OL,14,Fdiscovered her links to far-right
OL,15,Fgroups and extremism.
OL,17,FFive months before the attack she had
OL,18,Fused an online dating app to speak
OL,19,Fwith a man, who she told: "I am the
OL,20,Fembodiment of hell and desire to
OL,21,Famplify everything I bear witness too.
OL,26,@nD@\OUsD@cO]{D@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,F"I don't want to end my life anymore.
OL,7,FI plan on bringing change to the UK
OL,8,Fthrough means I can't detail."
OL,10,FShe later told him to "kill all the
OL,11,FJews and Muslims in Britain please".
OL,13,FThe man, who was not identified in
OL,14,Fcourt, reported the exchange to the
OL,15,Fpolice, the court was told.
OL,17,FDetectives found at her home
OL,18,Fhandwritten notes about the "spread of
OL,19,FIslam", how to use fertiliser to
OL,20,Fmanufacture explosives, and nuclear
OL,21,Fweapons.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@^O]rD@WOUsD@cO]zD@]OU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
