PN,43412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FThere were also notes about German SS
OL,7,Funits serving in the Second World War,
OL,8,FAdolf Hitler's book Mein Kampf, and
OL,9,Fthe nationalist novel The Turner
OL,10,FDiaries.
OL,12,FOn her notebook computer was a copy of
OL,13,Fa terrorist handbook with information
OL,14,Fabout chemicals and IEDs.
OL,16,FBurns had also used the Telegram
OL,17,Fmessaging app to contact a
OL,18,Frepresentative of the British far-
OL,19,Fright group Patriotic Alternative.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
