PN,43413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police say they've
OL,7,Ftaken steps to disrupt radical
OL,8,Factivity.
OL,10,FIn a victim personal statement Mr
OL,11,FMahmoodi said he had fled Iran because
OL,12,Fof persecution and had sought asylum
OL,13,Fin the UK.
OL,15,F"After this attack my life has
OL,16,Fcompletely changed," he said.
OL,18,F"I cannot move my neck easily and the
OL,19,Fphysical reminder of the scar where I
OL,20,Fwas nearly killed is a daily reminder.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@TO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
