OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,F"My mental health has suffered and I
OL,7,Fam living in fear.
OL,9,F"My sleep in impacted and I wake up
OL,10,Fwith bad dreams and nightmares of
OL,11,Fbeing attacked from behind with an axe.
OL,13,F"I am still living with the effects of
OL,14,Fthe attack more mentally than I could
OL,15,Fhave imagined."
OL,17,FAndrew Langdon KC, defending, said
OL,18,FBurns had experienced a difficult
OL,19,Fchildhood due to her family being made
OL,20,Fhomeless and living in a series of
OL,21,Ftemporary accommodation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
