PN,43415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1779098804
OL,3,CNeo-Nazi teen who tried to behead
OL,4,Cbarber jailed for more than 15 years
OL,6,F"This is plainly a disturbing case for
OL,7,Fa number of reasons," he said.
OL,9,F"My Ladyship's primary concern will be
OL,10,Ffor Mr Mahmoodi and for society."
OL,12,FMr Langdon said that despite both of
OL,13,FBurns's parents being teachers, the
OL,14,Fteenager had stopped attending full-
OL,15,Ftime education at 14.
OL,17,F"The last three of four years of her
OL,18,Flife are spiralling descent and
OL,19,Fisolation, despite living with her
OL,20,Ffamily," he added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@UO]qD@AOUrD@aO]yD@AOU|D@HO]
